{"tid":1105132,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)再造戰士1 3 4","createTime":"2019-04-13T16:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T20:05:05.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1ad4d73aeb0175e42b07f2cf2cb6b30e2c5d750c","tid":1105132,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T16:09:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8hphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a8a8dfae\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8hphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=3e979237\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8hphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=53ac89aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a>&lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/93/Universal_soldier_ver1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F93%2FUniversal_soldier_ver1.jpg&h=dde010a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.越戰後，美國政府進行了一項絕密的科學計劃。科學家們將越戰中犧牲的士兵的屍體冰凍起來，植入電腦晶片，輸入戰爭程序，將他們改造成為新一代的戰爭機器人――「再造戰士」，這些機器人沒有情感和以前的記憶，只有冰冷的殺戮武器。士兵盧克（尚格&middot;雲頓 Jean-Claude Van Damme 飾）和班長安德魯（杜夫&middot;朗格 Dolph Lundgren 飾）就是其中兩員，他們被派往參加一場新的戰爭。戰爭中，兩人的晶片突然出錯.....<br />\n<br />\n2.20世紀60年代，美國的勢力向亞洲滲透，為此政府實行的一項絕密計劃&mdash;&mdash;戰士再造計劃，通過藥物注射等手段將士兵大造成冷血無情、實力強悍的超級戰士。隨著技術不斷改進，在羅伯特&middot;柯林博士的主持下又開啟了白塔計劃，成功打造出更為完美的第二代超級戰士。然而一次意外後12名二代戰士逃亡，而涉嫌叛國的柯林博士也被驅逐東歐。此後不久，再造戰士佔領切爾諾貝利，美國軍方決定派出4名尚存的一代戰士前...<br />\n<br />\n3.約翰（史考特艾德金斯 飾）從昏迷中醒來後，發現他的妻女皆在家中被殘酷謀殺，他誓言追殺他依稀記得的兇手路克（尚克勞德范達美 飾），當他正努力拼湊記憶中的真相時，同時卻也被兇狠的再造戰士追緝。正當約翰一步步逼近路克，以安德魯（杜夫朗格 飾）為首並更強更猛的紅色大軍，也如從地獄歸來般迎接著他，約翰發現更多關於自己的事實，並開始質疑自己所相信的一切究竟是真是假？ <br />\n<br />\n12 15AM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8hphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=4d7992a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8hphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=fb40e81f\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97d5d74539b7af6efa1cf1c4f2e1a108c0edc2a2","tid":1105132,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b486c5946b83f0bfe1f3aeaa6f671e55e041d10","tid":1105132,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets